card_text: Tribute 1 Normal Monster or "Magikey" monster (except a Token), then target up to 2 Normal Monsters and/or "Magikey" monsters in your GY whose total Levels equal 8 or less; Special Summon those monsters in Defense Position, then you can apply 1 of the following effects immediately after this effect resolves.$N●Synchro Summon 1 "Magikey" Synchro Monster using monsters you control.$N●Xyz Summon 1 "Magikey" Xyz Monster using monsters you control.
